{
  "macro_id": "ops.analytics",
  "domain": "ops",
  "name": "analytics",
  "inputs": {
    "sinceDays": { "type": "number", "min": 1, "max": 3650 }
  },
  "invariants": [
    "typeof output === 'object' && output !== null",
    "typeof output.ok === 'boolean'",
    "output.ok === false || (typeof output.result.totalIncidents === 'number' && output.result.totalIncidents >= 0)",
    "output.ok === false || (typeof output.result.mttaMinutes === 'number' && typeof output.result.mttrMinutes === 'number')",
    "output.ok === false || Array.isArray(output.result.weeklyTrend)"
  ],
  "fuzz_cases": [
    { "input": {}, "expect": { "ok": true } },
    { "input": { "sinceDays": -1 }, "expect": { "ok": false, "error": "invalid_sinceDays" } },
    { "input": { "sinceDays": 30 }, "expect": { "ok": true } }
  ],
  "_note": "Computes MTTA/MTTR + per-severity + weekly-trend over the caller's incidents in per-user STATE. Empty store → all-zero metrics, weeklyTrend [] (NEVER no_db). sinceDays is a fail-CLOSED numeric guard — poisoned value → invalid_sinceDays, never a clamped ok:true."
}
